### 1. List Products
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/products?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Product Detail
# Replace {slug} with actual slug from list
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/products/test-product
Accept: application/json

### 3. Search Products
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/api/v1/products/search?q=t-shirt
Accept: application/json
